"{\"uid\": \"kswo.com-2024-08-09-lpd-partners-with-homeland-bagging-badges-event-raise-money-special-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"LAWTON, Okla. (KSWO) - The Lawton Police Department is partnering with a local homeland for the annual 'Bagging with Badges' event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 6, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawton_High_School\", \"score\": 0.9999997950151492, \"rank\": 1.927369076821428e-07, \"text\": \"LAWTON\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawton_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawton_High_School\"}, {\"begin\": 27, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawton_High_School\", \"score\": 0.999999795104166, \"rank\": 1.927369076821428e-07, \"text\": \"Lawton\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawton_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lawton_High_School\"}, {\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 51, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"score\": 0.9065894078429714, \"rank\": 0.09740131452800214, \"text\": \"Police Department\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Police\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From 9 a.m. to 1 p.m., officers with LPD will work with athletes to bag groceries to raise money for the upcoming Special Olympics.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amphibious_transport_dock\", \"score\": 0.9968704273546971, \"rank\": 0.003139394136912514, \"text\": \"LPD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amphibious_transport_dock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amphibious_transport_dock\"}, {\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.