\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you'd like to donate, you can catch officers and athletes at the Homeland location on 6734 NW Cache Road  Copyright 2024 KSWO.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": []}]}"